document_data.History:
''Circa'' [[1486 DR]], Olisara was near [[Hillsfar]] and hired an adventuring party to investigate some cases of kidnapped farmers in the area, which was possibly related to the [[Red Plumes]].{{Cite adventurers league/Shackles of Blood|8-9}}

Olisara was possibly involved in an expedition to [[Throstulgrael]]'s lair in the {{YearlinkName|1489}}. The Harper's objective was to recover the belongings of a Harper agent killed by the [[dragon]].

In the {{YearlinkName|1491}}, Olisara was in [[Mulmaster]] as a lead Harper agent for the [[Moonsea]] region and possibly asked some adventurers hired by [[Blade (disambiguation)|Blade]] [[Cora Peytir]] to save a member of the [[Cult of the Black Earth]] who wanted to defect to the Harpers.{{Cite adventurers league/Black Heart of Vengeance|17}}
